<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Apparition" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Apparition,</orth> significative appearance: <cit><quote>amazed at --s, signs and prodigies,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 926" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 926</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a thousand blushing --s to start into her face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 161</bibl></cit>. Especially sight of a spirit or spectre: <cit><quote>fine a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.317" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 317</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this monstrous a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.277" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 277</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.211" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 211</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>